 />\n二戰到依家美軍冇停過打仗"},{"pid":"2043b255c90a71569bd65f634ef0a50571a6405d","tid":921931,"uid":67876,"like":53,"dislike":5,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"我記得有人講過<br />\n打仗一定要用新兵去打<br />\n因為佢地咩尻都唔知 會幫你博命<br />\n反而老兵知道真正戰場好血腥<br />\n會打打吓縮沙<br />\n但無老兵教路新兵會好快痴線<br />\n所以短期打仗無問題<br />\n一拖到長期 解放軍仆直都似"},{"pid":"05e65d8285a0725eec79772cfd46832c5c59a86d","tid":921931,"uid":22694,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa6bcca7e047fa31e7d212130d8fa872d2b37f48","tid":921931,"uid":810,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:48:15.000Z","msg":"事實黎<br />\n二戰到依家美軍冇停過打仗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"根本每個年代都搵計開戰賺錢"},{"pid":"7133aa0b64290667a5b3a72f68820dc24071f37f","tid":921931,"uid":44698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:51:52.000Z","msg":"日日打緊飛機喎"},{"pid":"7850cf177ab7c1974f53021fbd8f6793a3b4ba86","tid":921931,"uid":10890,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"解放軍軍而家都開始唔夠人<br />\n一嚟少咗人願意參軍 話哂好多屋企得一粒仔<br />\n二嚟係啲人想參都過唔到體檢<br />\n長年累月食元素週期表 呼吸祖國空氣<br />\n你估真係冇後遺症<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCongratulations, you play yourself"},{"pid":"ab140b313cbe8c2eed9d97518e57ced5ab401c8a","tid":921931,"uid":107269,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"從來都唔信解放軍會打仗<br />\n<br />\n第一唔識打<br />\n第二，一開波，d 高官將領肯定第一個縮沙"},{"pid":"f0d1ebc9a5ac8945814291d0121a4a9b02f8cf2d","tid":921931,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dd96ff94acaf88eae6fe2b41f812220104627c4","tid":921931,"uid":25240,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"韓戰皇牌機師一個夠打三個美國兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx